---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | MyGreekTax"
  description="How MyGreekTax collects, uses, and protects your personal data."
  canonicalPath="/privacy/"
>
  <main style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:#28251d;">
    <a href="/" style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#C9923A;text-decoration:none;">← Back to MyGreekTax</a>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.5rem;margin:1.5rem 0 0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:#7a7974;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Last updated: 1 July 2026</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">1. Who We Are</h2>
    <p>MyGreekTax is operated by Dimitrios Gkikas, a licensed Greek tax professional. Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@mygreektax.eu" style="color:#C9923A;">hello@mygreektax.eu</a></p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">2. Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you submit the consultation form we collect your name, email address, and the details you provide. We do not collect payment information on this site.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>Your data is used solely to respond to your enquiry. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties except where required by law.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:2;">
      <li><strong>Make (Celonis Labs BV)</strong> — receives and routes consultation form submissions to our internal client system. See <a href="https://www.make.com/en/privacy-notice" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#C9923A;">their privacy policy</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Plausible Analytics</strong> — cookie-free, GDPR-compliant analytics. No personal data stored.</li>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — fonts loaded from Google's CDN; your IP may be logged by Google.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">5. Cookies</h2>
    <p>This site does not use tracking cookies. Plausible Analytics operates without cookies. See our <a href="/cookies/" style="color:#C9923A;">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, rectify, or erase any personal data we hold about you. Email <a href="mailto:hello@mygreektax.eu" style="color:#C9923A;">hello@mygreektax.eu</a>.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">7. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Enquiry data is retained for up to 3 years unless you request earlier deletion.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">8. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy occasionally. The "last updated" date at the top will reflect any changes.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
